rows.label: tlk42350122_04_msg0001
rows.name:
The people living in Torigo are so
kind. They're preparing a place for
people who suddenly arrived.

rows.label: tlk42350122_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Normally, when someone enters
your territory, a fight breaks
out, so it's amazing.

rows.label: tlk42350122_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I find turf wars to be a pain,
so I'd probably just give up
my spot without a fight.

rows.label: tlk42350122_04_msg0004
rows.name:
At this rate, I think the
newcomers will quickly fit in
and become friends with everyone.
